<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>zhǔ yé sū shuō tā kuài huí lái le 迦南1392</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ yé sū shuō tā kuài huí lái le. nà rì zi nà shí chén méi yǒu rén zhī dào,
 tiān shǐ bù zhī dào zi yě bù zhī dào, wéi yǒu fù zhī dào,
 nǐ men yào jǐn shèn jǐng xǐng qí dǎo, yīn wèi nǐ men yě bù zhī dào,
 zhǔ huí lái de shí hòu huò wǎn shàng huò bàn yè huò zǎo chén huò jī jiào,
 kǒng pà tā hū rán lái dào hū rán lái dào, kàn jiàn nǐ men shuì zhe le,
 zhǔ zǎo yǐ yù xiān tí chū jǐng gào, yào jǐng xǐng yào dǎo gào.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>1392</hymn_number>
</song>